":"mailto:theturingway@gmail.com","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"theturingway@gmail​.com","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"JWL2LCTMRs"}],"urlSource":"mailto:theturingway@gmail.com","key":"V7bhISvSsU"},{"type":"text","value":", or individually write to ","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"cl9oJKki3k"},{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Turing Way","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"jK0QkJGTjp"}],"key":"jeIl5h48TE"},{"type":"text","value":" team.","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"Z83RqbZ5UR"}],"key":"TiApWHhgLq"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We co-design the session with the co-hosts -- they are also the speaker in the session and we don’t have the moderator vs speaker differentiation.","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"xad50CqPtr"}],"key":"Dc26Ug2zNC"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We try to bring different views, perspectives and backgrounds through the speakers. We very much welcome suggestions and nominations for speakers.","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"key":"k3YaS19Go3"}],"key":"KspgsY1d6i"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We use Etherpad to share the format, invite everyone to share their notes and resources and take them back with them after the event.","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"pNDAEfniyW"}],"key":"JWBFP4tlQA"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Engaging via chat is optional, if you get distracted by the chats, please disable chat notifications.","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"PTbtpumLS3"}],"key":"o91resa2Jb"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"You can share your question via Etherpad or Zoom chat. Co-hosts will try to address them in the last part of the discussion. If we don’t have the time to address them live, we will make sure to respond via Etherpad.","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"sw925gJQgY"}],"key":"Hb99hJbtJm"}],"key":"ZT11BKMAAa"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Co-hosts - facilitate the session","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"RLE8GLRwJ7"}],"label":"ch-fireside-chat-roles-hosts","identifier":"ch-fireside-chat-roles-hosts","html_id":"ch-fireside-chat-roles-hosts","key":"D8tQSaEa5g"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Co-hosts are invited to co-design the event with one of ","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"BxlGX1eV5x"},{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Turing Way","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"I1M2WAZc17"}],"key":"xGNuCSa1lX"},{"type":"text","value":" team members.\nThey enable a discussion that does not look for answers or solutions but creates shared opportunities for members from different communities to explore a topic or challenge from their contexts.\nIf there are solutions available, that is great! But that is not the goal. The hope is that these discussions will stimulate ideas for collaboration beyond the Fireside Chats.\n","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"U6yze0LKi2"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We have 2 hosts for each session to allow hosts to also address questions, as well as share tasks such as coordinating with the speakers or monitoring questions.","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"w9g9FuwA6O"}],"key":"jESsCzqpmh"}],"key":"ofA3h0gA51"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"During the event, they will help each other keep track of time, and bring back discussions in the direction that they planned for if the discussion deviates. Support each other in taking audience questions. If due to a technical glitch, one of the hosts/speakers drops, they can continue with the planned agenda by themselves, or ask ","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"Kz49liV3Jh"},{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Turing Way","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"ynNVMhaPZs"}],"key":"GDcy28O0Dc"},{"type":"text","value":" team to step in to help as needed.","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"r0urlVCs9h"}],"key":"jZsAPoAkCe"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They get to set the tone and direction of the event and suggest/curate speakers for the panel. The suggested number of the complete panel is 5-6. Please consider diverse perspectives and experiences as well as geographical diversity to make sure we have a balanced discussion.","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"weAPqMgF5M"}],"key":"TYu7ZDiwbo"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Responsibilities of co-hosts: Supported by ","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"DrTeUw0IjS"},{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Turing Way","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"zSgEhHAWQt"}],"key":"MR9L0eBneh"},{"type":"text","value":" team where needed","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"pvSGGQBEFT"}],"key":"nwFXvU5NWo"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Co-hosts will represent their organisation/community at this event - and can choose to include their logo in the event’s promotional materials.","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"btR5nRcoS4"}],"key":"jXtDPhyYI7"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Share a short blurb about their organisation and a logo to be included on the Eventbrite page.","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"aY8o2G2kt1"}],"key":"O9ku0jMG5N"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Decide on the title - this will allow us to put together an Eventbrite page.","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"key":"kr7SLRTNki"}],"key":"XzTRJAwMun"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Decide on the speakers - they are invited and details are added on the Eventbrite page and other promotional material.","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"WcoaF96wHA"}],"key":"Xsx3tzA9zl"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"If they already know the suggested speaker, we will appreciate it if they can send the invitation and get confirmation using an ","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"la8MDv11RP"},{"type":"link","url":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/12VoVexsXXBx25SnAU4mayPw5un-v936g9Ux61DLjGzo/edit","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"email draft","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"x5l0mIKMLB"}],"urlSource":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/12VoVexsXXBx25SnAU4mayPw5un-v936g9Ux61DLjGzo/edit","key":"pohaJyhYys"},{"type":"text","value":".","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"THaY2C1SRs"}],"key":"uBbpLJqy1S"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Host 30 mins calls with the speakers before the event to identify what they would like to speak about.","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"Bg7E77nnGU"}],"key":"oG59osdhc9"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Frame questions based on their discussions with the speakers, and invite speakers to help finalise the questions (using Slack and the planning document).","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"VDOgtLUQvl"}],"key":"OG5LKm3Dzt"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Considering the flow of the discussion, decide on the order of the questions that will be asked.","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"SE2ZdbSmWt"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Each co-host should have equal opportunity to get ‘stage time’.","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"V04ajyCOWy"}],"key":"sBesNRzdLR"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They should agree on which questions they will pose to guide the discussion.","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"rLHvQ9jm4r"}],"key":"ztzt7Q1IO3"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They should pose 1 question to each speaker who takes a lead on responding. 1-2 follow-up responses can be invited from other speakers.","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"M9Ecc63KMj"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Make sure that the speakers know in what order they will be speaking, and what questions will be asked.","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"key":"KREuHYIRWk"}],"key":"Vc4fdxBaUO"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Coordinate via the Slack channel, and share any notes about the format via the shared document.","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"key":"kQwzQoo5be"}],"key":"hmbLN2yvvu"}],"key":"GpEzMqlRp2"}],"key":"y2pFVlTZPp"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They should pose at least one question to each other - either directly, or as a follow-up to the main question.","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"key":"vVapJZWuEP"}],"key":"jTHDl32KoF"}],"key":"CxcdIz5Qmo"}],"key":"N9HX2zb0vN"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Finalise a question for the closing statement (30-60 seconds take away from each speaker)","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"key":"RUDRLMCNmz"}],"key":"IbD0RVk0WL"}],"key":"KlVAeokngj"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Speakers - guide the discussion","position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"key":"Bn0klcyK8D"}],"label":"ch-fireside-chat-roles-speakers","identifier":"ch-fireside-chat-roles-speakers","html_id":"ch-fireside-chat-roles-speakers","key":"LF633jgQbD"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":49,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We host 5-6 speakers in the panel, which includes the facilitators.\nIt is important to note that Fireside Chats don’t have the traditional role of facilitators versus speakers.\nFacilitators are invited based on their experience on the topic and they also respond to questions, adding to the discussion from their experiences.","position":{"start":{"line":49,"column":1},"end":{"line":49,"column":1}},"key":"mh7sq2vNxp"}],"key":"Ay8tUXIqBE"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":65,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Once agreed upon, all speakers will be invited to join a private Slack channel to participate in asynchronous planning discussions.","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"key":"p4f7trRuZV"}],"key":"xltFupmqmh"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They will supply a short bio and image to be shared on the Eventbrite page.","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"key":"NS8eVRUB95"}],"key":"fkfzwlA4e0"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They will be invited to attend a call (30) minutes before the event to discuss the topic and help the co-hosts identify what specific area of the topic they will talk about.","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"key":"mVBcBuwuMw"}],"key":"gsqw770o8K"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1},"end":{"line":56,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They will be coordinating with the co-host to finalise the specific question posed to them, and if they would like, they can suggest another question for the other panellists.","position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1},"end":{"line":56,"column":1}},"key":"VufkR8nZ84"}],"key":"zQ7A3k3DhB"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They will have access to the internal planning documents where they can find all information they need, as well as have opportunities to give feedback by directly collaborating on the Google document.","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"key":"lz8vIfQZu7"}],"key":"RQSdWUcJAl"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1},"end":{"line":58,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They should check what in addition to questions posed to them, questions they would like to respond to as a follow-up discussion.","position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1},"end":{"line":58,"column":1}},"key":"c2WyU8ZRJ1"}],"key":"R9Aa0Dtzgy"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Join Zoom at least 5-10 minutes before the event to test their system (microphone, camera, internet, and access to the document used for the session).","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"key":"T9ecXnn2To"}],"key":"AuJ8jj29Mz"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":60,"column":1},"end":{"line":60,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It is important that all speakers get the same ‘stage time’. (If you are the speaker -- please take this space to share your thoughts if you are generally not the one speaking out, and if you generally tend to speak more, please intentionally create space for others to speak).","position":{"start":{"line":60,"column":1},"end":{"line":60,"column":1}},"key":"rynYn3dgOe"}],"key":"Nw72QGN